{"tid":660931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人知個套乜報仇者同盟有乜野咁巴鳩閉?","createTime":"2018-05-11T06:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T12:50:08.000Z","uid":76115,"like":4,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"44dda12d08eea9ac3cb054ca0fa36cb05ca86179","tid":660931,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:11:07.000Z","msg":"我無睇過唔知套戲咩料<br />\n但睇到班fans見親人批評就話要睇哂佢唔知幾多十年製作, 幾百年前文後理, 屌你擺到明商業片一套梗係要預左大半觀眾乜都唔知入去睇架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講到要做哂功課咁, 而家睇超級英雄片定睇康德三大批判呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己熟個唔知咩系列少少就話其他人唔識尊重套戲, 唔尊重製作心血, 睇套爛鳩爆炸打鬥大波妹肌肉男荷里活片睇到要沐浴焚香咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6541f861c27887619646bef785a82607e654c74","tid":660931,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:20:05.000Z","msg":"本來好撚憎單春迅呢條奶共造作狗, 但睇到佢兩句野激到班唔知咩盟fans生蝦咁跳真係幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27b308fbdbad32c8391700200ce2c9daa4b51c4","tid":660931,"uid":82224,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:21:29.000Z","msg":"Ching 想出位，但遲左好多步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81f98897fb06f73f1bc1b9812a5381073869350","tid":660931,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:24:17.000Z","msg":"Ching冇撚錯,同盟真係幾爛嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/1/16/%E5%90%8C%E7%9B%9F.jpg/250px-%E5%90%8C%E7%9B%9F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F1%2F16%2F%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%259B%259F.jpg%2F250px-%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%259B%259F.jpg&h=c45ce0fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"197de3e54ae2c58147407e1dcf7bcdb24d84ef2a","tid":660931,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c27b308fbdbad32c8391700200ce2c9daa4b51c4","tid":660931,"uid":82224,"lik